  "title": "Clinic Executive / Assistant (Camden)",
  "description": "<p><strong>This position is based at our clinic at Camden Centre.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities and Duties</strong></p>\n<p>-Manage reception area</p>\n<p>-Attend to clients and perform front-desk duties such as:</p>\n<p>-Registration</p>\n<p>-Appointment scheduling</p>\n<p>-Billing</p>\n<p>-Answering phone calls</p>\n<p>-Arranging bookings for Radiology and Laboratory</p>\n<p>tests</p>\n<p>-Handle blood/urine/stool samples and liaise with Laboratory/specimens collection and delivery</p>\n<p>-Process prescriptions accurately and dispense medicines</p>\n<p>-Process billing transactions under different</p>\n<p>Government schemes and managed care programmes</p>\n<p>-Answer client inquiries, provide information, assurance, and financial counselling</p>\n<p>-Assist the Doctor in chaperoning clients, if required</p>\n<p>-Manage stock and inventory</p>\n<p>-Operate Clinic Management System</p>\n<p>-Perform basic health screening assessments, including:</p>\n<p>-Height, weight, blood pressure</p>\n<p>-Waist, hip measurement, body fat analysis</p>\n<p>-Vision testing and Electrocardiogram (ECG) test</p>\n<p>-Maintain general cleanliness of the clinic</p>\n<p>-Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned</p>",
