    "description": "<p>OUR VISION<br>\nATA, translated from Hebrew, means \"you\". At ATA Medical, we believe every individual deserves to achieve physical wellness with up to date evidence based healthcare provision.<br>\nWe aim to improve the health of our nation, moving away from conventional “one package fits all” health screening, and bringing affordable bespoke screening and treatment to our patients.<br>\n<br>\nOUR VALUES<br>\nACTIVE<br>\nWe believe in an ACTIVE approach in ensuring our client's interests and outcome with us are optimised.<br>\n<br>\nTECHNOLOGY<br>\nWe utilize TECHNOLOGY in medicine to bring about evidenced based care and remote patient care.<br>\n<br>\nADAPTABILITY<br>\nGiven the ever changing medical knowledge, we believe in our ADAPTABILITY in achieving holistic care for patients.</p>",
